      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * Stanford University</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Stanford_Campus_Aerial_Photo.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Stanford_Campus_Aerial_Photo.JPG/330px-Stanford_Campus_Aerial_Photo.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Stanford_Campus_Aerial_Photo.JPG/500px-Stanford_Campus_Aerial_Photo.JPG 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/28/Stanford_Campus_Aerial_Photo.JPG/960px-Stanford_Campus_Aerial_Photo.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Stanford_Campus_Aerial_Photo.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Stanford University's campus <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Stanford University</b>, <br />\na private research university in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stanford,_California\">Stanford</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/California\">California</a>, and one of the world's most prestigious institutions, with the top position in numerous rankings and measures in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States\">United States</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.  \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Chess_Programs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Programs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Matches\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Matches</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"People\">People</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stanford_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: People\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Ashton_Anderson\" title=\"Ashton Anderson\">Ashton Anderson</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Louis_Chatriot&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Louis Chatriot (page does not exist)\">Louis Chatriot</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jens_Christensen\" title=\"Jens Christensen\">Jens Christensen</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/L._Stephen_Coles\" title=\"L. Stephen Coles\">L. Stephen Coles</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Truman_Collins\" title=\"Truman Collins\">Truman Collins</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Stuart_Cracraft\" title=\"Stuart Cracraft\">Stuart Cracraft</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Alvin_M._Despain\" title=\"Alvin M. Despain\">Alvin M. Despain</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/David_Eppstein\" title=\"David Eppstein\">David Eppstein</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Edward_Feigenbaum\" title=\"Edward Feigenbaum\">Edward Feigenbaum</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Derek_Farren&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Derek Farren (page does not exist)\">Derek Farren</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Richard_Fikes\" title=\"Richard Fikes\">Richard Fikes</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Samuel_Fuller\" title=\"Samuel Fuller\">Samuel Fuller</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Michael_Genesereth\" title=\"Michael Genesereth\">Michael Genesereth</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Matthew_L._Ginsberg\" title=\"Matthew L. Ginsberg\">Matthew L. Ginsberg</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=David_Gleich&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"David Gleich (page does not exist)\">David Gleich</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bill_Gosper\" title=\"Bill Gosper\">Bill Gosper</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Thomas_Hubert\" title=\"Thomas Hubert\">Thomas Hubert</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Nishith_Khandwala\" title=\"Nishith Khandwala\">Nishith Khandwala</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Donald_Knuth\" title=\"Donald Knuth\">Donald Knuth</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jan_Eric_Larsson\" title=\"Jan Eric Larsson\">Jan Eric Larsson</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Barbara_Liskov\" title=\"Barbara Liskov\">Barbara Liskov</a>, née Barbara Huberman</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Sanjoy_Mahajan\" title=\"Sanjoy Mahajan\">Sanjoy Mahajan</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/John_McCarthy\" title=\"John McCarthy\">John McCarthy</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/John_Moussouris\" title=\"John Moussouris\">John Moussouris</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Todd_W._Neller\" title=\"Todd W. Neller\">Todd W. Neller</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Barak_Oshri\" title=\"Barak Oshri\">Barak Oshri</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ryan_Porter\" title=\"Ryan Porter\">Ryan Porter</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Paul_S._Rosenbloom&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Paul S. Rosenbloom (page does not exist)\">Paul S. Rosenbloom</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Stuart_Russell\" title=\"Stuart Russell\">Stuart Russell</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Arthur_Samuel\" title=\"Arthur Samuel\">Arthur Samuel</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ilya_Sutskever\" title=\"Ilya Sutskever\">Ilya Sutskever</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Templeton&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Daniel Templeton (page does not exist)\">Daniel Templeton</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Sebastian_Thrun\" title=\"Sebastian Thrun\">Sebastian Thrun</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Meiji_Wang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Meiji Wang (page does not exist)\">Meiji Wang</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/David_Wilkins\" title=\"David Wilkins\">David Wilkins</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Programs\">Chess Programs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stanford_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Programs\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Les-bourgeois-de-Calais.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/86/Les-bourgeois-de-Calais.jpg/330px-Les-bourgeois-de-Calais.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"222\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/86/Les-bourgeois-de-Calais.jpg/500px-Les-bourgeois-de-Calais.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/86/Les-bourgeois-de-Calais.jpg/960px-Les-bourgeois-de-Calais.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Les-bourgeois-de-Calais.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Burghers_of_Calais\">Les Bourgeois de Calais</a> by <a href=\"/Category:Auguste_Rodin\" title=\"Category:Auguste Rodin\">Auguste Rodin</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Huberman\" title=\"Huberman\">Huberman</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Kotok-McCarthy-Program\" title=\"Kotok-McCarthy-Program\">Kotok-McCarthy-Program</a> developed at <a href=\"/Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology\" title=\"Massachusetts Institute of Technology\">MIT</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Paradise\" title=\"Paradise\">Paradise</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ConvChess\" title=\"ConvChess\">ConvChess</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Matches\">Matches</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stanford_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Matches\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Stanford-ITEP_Match\" title=\"Stanford-ITEP Match\">Stanford-ITEP Match</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stanford_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stanford_University\">Stanford University from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.stanford.edu/\">Stanford University</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://infolab.stanford.edu/pub/voy/museum/phototour.html\">Computer History Exhibits Photo Tour</a> created January 2000 by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://infolab.stanford.edu/~gio/\">Gio Wiederhold</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://engineering.stanford.edu/2010-stanford-engineering-heroes\">2010 Stanford Engineering Heroes</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/stanforduniversity\">Stanford University</a> channel on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stanford_University&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stanford_University\">Stanford University from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stanford_University\">Stanford University from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://infolab.stanford.edu/pub/voy/museum/samuel.html\">Arthur Samuel: Pioneer in Machine Learning</a> by <a href=\"/John_McCarthy\" title=\"John McCarthy\">John McCarthy</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://infolab.stanford.edu/pub/voy/museum.html\">Stanford Computer History Exhibits</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Burghers_of_Calais\">Les Bourgeois de Calais</a> by <a href=\"/Category:Auguste_Rodin\" title=\"Category:Auguste Rodin\">Auguste Rodin</a> in the Memorial Court of the Main Quad, on the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stanford_University\">Stanford University campus</a>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Les-bourgeois-de-Calais.jpg\">Photo</a> taken September 2004 by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Introvert\">Introvert</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikimedia_Commons\">Wikimedia Commons</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228163820\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.141 seconds\nReal time usage: 1.231 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 79/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 170/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:2233-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228163819 and revision id 24817\n -->\n"
